h-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">08:00 - 17:00</span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:right;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">address</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:right;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">25 Barzel Street, Tel Aviv</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:right;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">6971035</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:right;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Israel</span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_9 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:13px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\"><span class=\"color_11 wixui-rich-text__text\">© Copyright - Control Applications Ltd</span></span></p></div>\n<figure class=\"content-image\"><img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/9a8771_df05eef3a2a94d5bbd9d4f08dcef0334~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_280,h_52,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/Screen%2520Shot%25202021-01-20%2520at%252022_15_.png\" alt=\"Screen%20Shot%202021-01-20%20at%2022.15_\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"content-image\"><img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/9a8771_61c7f5da63404e9087760beddb4fc03c~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_369,h_367,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/elnet-xp-controller.png\" alt=\"elnet-xp-controller.png\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>",
  "rich_text": [
    "Elnet xp controller for drainage and sewage pumps",
    "An automatic switching controller is used to operate drainage and sewage pumps and is found in almost every public building today, the controller is used to automatically control the level of rainwater or sewage, including automatic switching between two pumps in each operation in order to balance the working hours and the introduction of an off-duty pump for reinforcement when necessary.\n​\nWe find these systems in factories, hotels, hospitals, universities, office buildings and any other public building where a reliable system is required to operate pumps for draining rainwater or sewage.\n​\nmain features\nFriendly operation in the Hebrew language using a colorful graphic screen.\nRegistration and display of documentation in time of up to 1000 alerts and events.\nRunning an off-duty pump to boost at a high level.\nAutomatic replacement in order to balance the working hours.\nPrevention of idle operations resulting from vibration of floats.\nChanging the operation delay in an easy and simple way.\nRS485 Modbus structure control communication (TCP/IP option).\nShort pump refresh after prolonged system shutdown.\nOperating pumps in non-return or float failure situations.\nAlgorithm for solving problems in unusual situations of recurring El.\nA command to activate a horn in a fault.\nCessation of fault horn operation after a changeable period of time.\nWiring test software includes a record in the event report that the wiring has been tested.\nTwo 150ma dry contact outputs for general fault and surf fault.",
    "Related Products",
    "Control Applications Ltd",
    "making contact\nPhone: +972-3-6474998\n​\nFax: +972-3-6474598\nEmail:\ncal@ddc.co.il",
    "opening hours\nControl Applications Ltd\nSunday - Thursday\n08:00 - 17:00",
    "Address\n25 Barzel Street, Tel Aviv\n6971035\nIsrael",
    "© Copyright - Control Applications Ltd"
  ],
